. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF44B1E9402FFD8BAE03C3BFE0BF9E6" author="Suffrian, E." box="[232,406,1585,1612]" pageId="13" pageNumber="264" pagination="1 - 483" refId="ref25218" refString="Suffrian, E. (1866) Zur Kenntnis der Sudamerikanischen Cryptocephalen. Linnaea Entomologica, 16, 1 - 483." type="journal article" year="1866">Suffrian (1866)</bibRefCitation>
did not mention the number of specimens under study but stated that no males were available for study. He reported the name of a single collector (“Sello”), a single locality (“Caasapava”) and MNHUB as single type location (depository), where 
<specimenCount id="9D63FD669402FFD8B8803C73FD71F939" box="[648,748,1657,1683]" pageId="13" pageNumber="264" type="female">3 female</specimenCount>
<typeStatus id="54DE884D9402FFD8B8FD3C70FCCAF93E" box="[757,855,1658,1684]" pageId="13" pageNumber="264">syntypes</typeStatus>
were found. A 
<typeStatus id="54DE884D9402FFD8BE043C73FBEEF939" box="[1036,1139,1657,1683]" pageId="13" pageNumber="264">lectotype</typeStatus>
is here designated as follows: 
<typeStatus id="54DE884D9402FFD8BAD33C97FEDFF91D" box="[219,322,1693,1719]" pageId="13" pageNumber="264">lectotype</typeStatus>
(by present designation): 
<specimenCount id="9D63FD669402FFD8B86C3C94FDE4F912" box="[612,633,1694,1720]" pageId="13" pageNumber="264" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
, pinned // “23947” [white label, printed] // “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C654D6C9402FFD8BE6F3C97FAA9F91D" authority="Suffr." authorityName=", Suffrian" authorityYear="1866" box="[1127,1332,1693,1719]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Metallactus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="264" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="planipennis">planipennis Suffr.</taxonomicName>
* Cassap: Sellow.” [blue label, handwritten] // “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C654D6C9402FFD8B8483CCBFC65F971" authority="Suffrian, 1866" authorityName=", Suffrian" authorityYear="1866" box="[576,1016,1729,1755]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Metallactus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="264" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="planipennis">
<emphasis id="B911EAFD9402FFD8B8483CCBFCD2F971" box="[576,847,1729,1755]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="264">Metallactus planipennis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFF44B1E9402FFD8B95E3CCBFC65F971" author="Suffrian, E." box="[854,1016,1729,1755]" pageId="13" pageNumber="264" pagination="1 - 483" refId="ref25218" refString="Suffrian, E. (1866) Zur Kenntnis der Sudamerikanischen Cryptocephalen. Linnaea Entomologica, 16, 1 - 483." type="journal article" year="1866">Suffrian, 1866</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
<subScript id="17E134AA9402FFD8BE083CC3FBE0F970" attach="right" box="[1024,1149,1737,1754]" fontSize="7" pageId="13" pageNumber="264">
<typeStatus id="54DE884D9402FFD8BE083CC3FBE0F970" box="[1024,1149,1737,1754]" pageId="13" pageNumber="264">LECTOTYPUS</typeStatus>
</subScript>
D. Sassi des.” [red label, printed] // (MNHUB). 
<typeStatus id="54DE884D9402FFD8BB943CEFFDD9F955" box="[412,580,1765,1791]" pageId="13" pageNumber="264">Paralectotypes</typeStatus>
: 2f 
<specimenCount id="9D63FD669402FFD8B8663CEFFDE3F955" box="[622,638,1765,1791]" pageId="13" pageNumber="264" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
, pinned, no labels on the pins, but they obviously belong to the same series of the LT. Label information and the number of 
<typeStatus id="54DE884D9402FFD8B8E73D00FCCCF88E" box="[751,849,1802,1828]" pageId="13" pageNumber="264">syntypes</typeStatus>
match the registration data from the old catalogue of the MNHUB (“23947 
<taxonomicName id="4C654D6C9402FFD8BB863D27FD7DF8ED" authority="Suffr." authorityName=", Suffrian" authorityYear="1866" box="[398,736,1837,1863]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Metallactus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="264" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="planipennis">Metallactus planipennis Suffr.</taxonomicName>
* 3. Cassapava, Sello”). Both 
<typeStatus id="54DE884D9402FFD8BE2D3D27FB5AF8ED" box="[1061,1223,1837,1863]" pageId="13" pageNumber="264">paralectotypes</typeStatus>
labeled as follows: // “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C654D6C9402FFD8BAB23D5BFD1EF8C6" authority="(Suffrian, 1866)" baseAuthorityName="Suffrian" baseAuthorityYear="1866" box="[186,643,1873,1900]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Metallactus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="264" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="planipennis">
